# 120 Peasants occupy landowners in Chapada Diamantina - The New Democracy

Author: Gabriel Artur

Description: In the early hours of March 1, about 120 peasants occupied the Santa Maria Farm, in the municipality of Itaberaba, in the region of Chapada Diamantina (BA).

