# More than 1,000 strikes occurred in 2022, reveals Dieese - the new democracy

Author: Giovanna Maria

Description: In 2022, the Intersindical Department of Statistics and Socioeconomic Studies (Dieese) recorded 1,067 strikes, which counted 54,000 hours

Publish Time: 2023-03-03T17:39:00-03:00

Modified Time: 2023-03-03T18:04:15-03:00

Updated Time: 2023-03-03T18:04:15-03:00

Images: ['[IMG_1067-801.jpg](https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/IMG_1067-801.jpg)', '[svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxOTQiIGhlaWdodD0iMzAiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCAxOTQgMzAiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIHN0eWxlPSJmaWxsOiNjZmQ0ZGI7ZmlsbC1vcGFjaXR5OiAwLjE7Ii8+PC9zdmc+](https://anovademocracia.com.brdata:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxOTQiIGhlaWdodD0iMzAiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCAxOTQgMzAiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIHN0eWxlPSJmaWxsOiNjZmQ0ZGI7ZmlsbC1vcGFjaXR5OiAwLjE7Ii8+PC9zdmc+)', '[svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0NDMiIGhlaWdodD0iMjk2IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNDQzIDI5NiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgc3R5bGU9ImZpbGw6I2NmZDRkYjtmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk6IDAuMTsiLz48L3N2Zz4=](https://anovademocracia.com.brdata:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0NDMiIGhlaWdodD0iMjk2IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNDQzIDI5NiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgc3R5bGU9ImZpbGw6I2NmZDRkYjtmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk6IDAuMTsiLz48L3N2Zz4=)', '[svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI3OTAiIGhlaWdodD0iNDM2IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNzkwIDQzNiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgc3R5bGU9ImZpbGw6I2NmZDRkYjtmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk6IDAuMTsiLz48L3N2Zz4=](https://anovademocracia.com.brdata:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI3OTAiIGhlaWdodD0iNDM2IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNzkwIDQzNiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgc3R5bGU9ImZpbGw6I2NmZDRkYjtmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk6IDAuMTsiLz48L3N2Zz4=)']

Section: Nacional

Tags: ['2022', 'dieese', 'greve', 'Luta Classista']

Type: article

<!--METADATA-->

![](Images/A Nova Democracia/2023-03-03T17-39-00-03-00/IMG_1067-801.jpg)Nurses performed a large protest at Avenida Presidente Vargas, in Rio de Janeiro, in 2022, in the fight for their salary floor. Photo: Database and

![Print friendly, pdf & email](Images/A Nova Democracia/2023-03-03T17-39-00-03-00/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxOTQiIGhlaWdodD0iMzAiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCAxOTQgMzAiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIHN0eWxlPSJmaWxsOiNjZmQ0ZGI7ZmlsbC1vcGFjaXR5OiAwLjE7Ii8+PC9zdmc+)In 2022, the Intersindical Department of Statistics and Socioeconomic Studies(Dieese)It recorded 1,067 strikes, which counted 54,000 hours. Amaior of these strikes was in order to combat attacks on already established rights. The department states that in 2022, the number of strikes seequipped to 2019, before the COVI-19 pandemic, noting that in this member, the large companies used the relative demobilization of workers to deepen the precariousness at work, promoting dedicated cuts and outsourcing in large scale.

The claims of 81% of strikes were related to labor attacks, representing a total of 866 strikes. Within dismissal, more than half(51%)He referred to the denunciation of non-compliance with about 547 strikes. Another 46% were strikes against the degradation of working conditions, with 493 strikes.

Many of the strikes also had as guidelines the conquest or amplication dedicated and benefits. The percentage was 49.6%, about 529 strikes.

In addition, about 15.5%, or 165 strikes, were strikes of “protest”, described by the Dieese as a strike that “aims to meet claims that go beyond the scope of labor relations”.

![](Images/A Nova Democracia/2023-03-03T17-39-00-03-00/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0NDMiIGhlaWdodD0iMjk2IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNDQzIDI5NiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgc3R5bGU9ImZpbGw6I2NmZDRkYjtmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk6IDAuMTsiLz48L3N2Zz4=)##### ** out of 5 strikes, 2 were by salaries **

Among the greatest claims were salary issues such as readjustment(42%)and floor payment(27%), the most frequent. Items Related to Food(Tickets, Basic Baskets)and the payment of arrears(salaries, 13th, vacation)Then came, with the participation of 20%.Strikes that covered whole professional categories(53%)they were prepaid in relation to those performed in isolation by companies(private or state -owned)or units(47%).

De acordo com o Dieese, o quadro de greves de 2022 é mais semelhante ao do anode 2019, uma vez que nos anos de 2020 e 2021, devido à pandemia, houve umrefluxo na mobilização. Traçando um comparativo, de 2021 a 2022, aparticipação de greves deflagradas por funcionários públicos aumentou 196%.

Além disso, sobre a precarização do trabalho nesse meio tempo, o departamentodiscorre que a “flexibilização forçada que a pandemia inaugurou/acentuou emmuitas organizações passaria a ser utilizada sistematicamente como um meioeficaz de precarização do trabalho, cujas possibilidades, é verdade, jáestavam dadas antes de 2019, mas que não haviam sido testadas em talamplitude”.

Para exemplificar, pega-se o caso do Santander, que segundo denúncia dossindicatos, funcionários diretos estavam sendo transferidos em número cada vezmaior para empresas prestadoras de serviço que, mesmo sob a administração dobanco, não assinam a Convenção Coletiva dos Bancários. Terceirizados à força,os trabalhadores estão, dessa forma, sujeitos a uma grande perda de direitos.

#####  **Bomba relógio**

![](Images/A Nova Democracia/2023-03-03T17-39-00-03-00/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI3OTAiIGhlaWdodD0iNDM2IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNzkwIDQzNiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgc3R5bGU9ImZpbGw6I2NmZDRkYjtmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk6IDAuMTsiLz48L3N2Zz4=)The class struggle in Brazil is constantly a bomb about to explode. Axploitation and oppression of workers are particularly serious in the country, due to their condition of semicolonial, dependent and subjugated to the imperialism, that each crisis deepens prey over our people. Essecenary was deeply aggravated after the pension reform presented in 2016, followed by the labor reform in 2017.

Workers' mobilizations are a direct reflection of the attack on the rights perpetrator labor reform. In it, points were approved such as: authorization from Collective Disesse without union intervention; permission for "collective" negotiation of less beneficial conditions to the worker than those provided for(for example, the extension of the workday in an unhealthy environment); overtime without payment in "Home Office", among other attacks.As for the new government, the National Directory of the Workers Party(PT)Approves “to see” documents that say “defending the revocation of labor contracting in the Temer government”, while Luiz Inacio leaves it to reject the idea of “changing everything and returning to what it was before”, that is, to really revoke the reform.

In turn, Rui Costa, his Minister of the Civil House, states that "there is no proposal of revision of the ongoing social security reform."

Given this, it enters 2023 with thousands of strikes across the country, expressing this explosive situation. Only between January and early March, there were strikes from [teachers](https://anovademocracia.com.br/professores-realizam-greves-e-protestos-exigindo-reajuste-salarial-em-todo-pais/), from [nurses](https://anovademocracia.com.br/dia-nacional-de-mobilizacao-de-enfermeiros-exige-o-piso-salarial/), of [metalurgical workers](https://anovademocracia.com.br/sp-metalurgicos-em-greve-exigem-pagamento-atrasado-com-protestos-em-frente-a-fabrica/), [Metroviaries](https://anovademocracia.com.br/mg-metroviarios-mantem-greve-que-ja-dura-tres-semanas-com-100-de-paralisacao/), [Drivers of Modes](https://anovademocracia.com.br/mg-motoristas-de-onibus-em-greve-exigem-salario-digno/), [Deliveners and Drop Drivers](https://anovademocracia.com.br/entregadores-de-aplicativo-realizam-protestos-e-greves/)and [public servants](https://anovademocracia.com.br/protestos-de-servidores-em-todo-pais-exigem-direitos/).

News Source: [https://anovademocracia.com.br/mais-de-mil-greves-ocorreram-em-2022-revela-dieese/](https://anovademocracia.com.br/mais-de-mil-greves-ocorreram-em-2022-revela-dieese/)

