# Civilian community, shot by 94th IB; houses damaged

Author: Philippine Revolution Web Central

Publish Time: 2023-03-03T97:00:00-04:00

Modified Time: None

Description: Farmers' homes Albascion Onopre and Rhoda Garnica in Sitio Cabagnaan, Barangay Carabalan, Himamaylan City, Negros Occidental were damaged after being shot dead by a bullet of 94T soldiers

Images: ['[ang-bayan-dailies-human-rights-violations-hrvs-1024x502.png](https://philippinerevolution.nu/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/ang-bayan-dailies-human-rights-violations-hrvs-1024x502.png)']

Categories: ['Human Rights']

Type: article

<!--METADATA-->

![](Images/Philippine Revolution Web Central/2023-03-03T97-00-00-04-00/ang-bayan-dailies-human-rights-violations-hrvs-1024x502.png )Farmers' homes Albascion onopre and Rhoda Garnica Sasityo Cabagnaan, Barangay Carabalan, Himamaylan City, Negros Occidental after a gunshot wound to the 94th IB soldiers on March 1. According to September 21 Movement South Negros, soldiers fired after reporting that encounter between the 94th IB and the unit of the new army in an area covered by the Sitio.

The group said the sympathy of civilians and civilian communities was a violation of the Comprehensive Agreement on Respect of Human Rights and InternationalHumanitarian Law or CAHRIHL signed by representatives of the Government of thePilipinas and the National Democratic Front of the Philippines.

The shooting caused the shooting to the residents. "The homeowners ... hurried to hide so that they would not be hit.

On that day, about 100 families fled to the center of Barangay Mulasa Sitio of Panagbaan, Florete, Cabalungan, and Daat. The military also controls and monitors the actions of those in the evacuation center. They are slowly getting back now.

Residents reported the continued harassment and threat of the military to civilians. They said they were shouting "If it's a shout, let's go!"(Whoever is brave there, come out!)and "the inhabitants"(Will spend the people here).

Ang ginagawang karahasan ng militar laban mga sibilyan ay labag sa Ika-4 naBahagi, Artikulo 4, Numero 4 ng CARHRIHL:

"Ang sibilyang populasyon at mga sibilyan ay itatrato bilang sibilyan at ipag-iiba sa mga mandirigma at, kasama ang kanilang ari-arian, ay hindi maaaringatakihin."

